Date: 1998-03-20

Title: SU(2) Poisson-Lie T duality

Authors: M.A. Lledo and V.S.V. Varadarajan

Comments: 12 pages, 1 figure

Journal-ref: Lett.Math.Phys. 45 (1998) 247-257

Poisson-Lie target space duality is a framework where duality transformationsare properly defined. In this letter we investigate the pair of sigma modelsdefined by the double SO(3,1) in the Iwasawa decomposition.